---
description: Setup dan pembuatan aplikasi Kewer Koperasi - Sistem Pinjaman Modal Pedagang
---

## Project Overview
**Nama Project**: Kewer Koperasi  
**Deskripsi**: Sistem pinjaman modal pedagang digital (bisnis perorangan, bukan koperasi berbadan hukum)  
**Target**: Pedagang pasar, warung, UMKM informal  
**Owner**: Pemilik tunggal dengan beberapa cabang dan petugas lapangan  

## Setup Environment

### 1. Start XAMPP
```bash
cd /opt/lampp
echo "8208" | sudo -S ./xampp start
```

### 2. Database Setup
```bash
# Database sudah dibuat: kewer_koperasi
# Password MySQL: root
# Tables sudah diimport: cabang, users, nasabah, petugas, pinjaman, angsuran, pembayaran, tabungan
```

### 3. Dependencies
```bash
# PHP 8.2.12 sudah terinstall dengan extensions: mysqli, gd, json
# Composer sudah diinstall di /usr/local/bin/composer
```

## Project Structure
```
kewer-app/
|-- config/
|   |-- database.php      # Konfigurasi database
|   |-- session.php       # Session management
|   `-- config.php        # Konfigurasi umum
|-- includes/
|   |-- header.php        # Header template
|   |-- footer.php        # Footer template
|   |-- sidebar.php       # Sidebar navigation
|   |-- functions.php     # Fungsi-fungsi core
|   `-- auth.php          # Autentikasi
|-- api/
|   |-- index.php         # Router API
|   |-- nasabah.php       # API nasabah
|   |-- pinjaman.php      # API pinjaman
|   |-- angsuran.php      # API angsuran
|   `-- auth.php          # API autentikasi
|-- pages/
|   |-- dashboard.php     # Dashboard utama
|   |-- login.php         # Login page
|   |-- nasabah/          # Modul nasabah
|   |   |-- index.php     # List nasabah
|   |   |-- tambah.php    # Tambah nasabah
|   |   |-- detail.php    # Detail nasabah
|   |   |-- edit.php      # Edit nasabah
|   |   `-- transfer.php  # Transfer nasabah
|   |-- pinjaman/         # Modul pinjaman
|   |-- angsuran/        # Modul angsuran
|   |-- petugas/          # Modul petugas
|   `-- cabang/           # Modul cabang
|-- assets/
|   |-- css/              # CSS files
|   |-- js/               # JavaScript files
|   `-- images/           # Image assets
|-- uploads/              # File uploads (KTP, foto selfie)
|-- .windsurf             # File ini (workflow documentation)
|-- .htaccess            # Apache configuration
|-- composer.json         # Dependencies
|-- login.php             # Entry point login
|-- dashboard.php         # Entry point dashboard
`-- index.php             # Entry point utama
```

## Default Login
- **Super Admin**: admin / admin123
- **Manager Cabang A**: mgr_a / manager123
- **Manager Cabang B**: mgr_b / manager123

