## Development Workflow

### 1. Copy Code Boilerplate
```bash
# Copy dari kurasi-koperasi-pasar.md Section 16
# Extract code blocks dan save ke appropriate files
```

### 2. Configuration
```bash
# Update config/database.php dengan credentials:
# DB_HOST: localhost
# DB_NAME: kewer_koperasi
# DB_USER: root
# DB_PASS: root
```

### 3. Testing
```bash
# Access via browser:
# http://localhost/kewer-app/login.php
```

## Security Notes
- Password hashing dengan bcrypt
- SQL injection prevention dengan prepared statements
- Session timeout
- File upload validation
- Role-based access control

## Troubleshooting

### XAMPP Issues
```bash
# Check status
cd /opt/lampp
./xampp status

# Restart services
echo "8208" | sudo -S ./xampp restart
```

### Database Issues
```bash
# Check connection
/opt/lampp/bin/mysql -u root --password="root" -e "SELECT DATABASE();"

# Reset database (if needed)
/opt/lampp/bin/mysql -u root --password="root" -e "DROP DATABASE kewer_koperasi; CREATE DATABASE kewer_koperasi;"
```

### File Permissions
```bash
# Fix permissions
chmod 755 -R /opt/lampp/htdocs/kewer-app
chmod 777 /opt/lampp/htdocs/kewer-app/uploads
```

